    "In general healthcare, the LLM technology is now widely acclaimed for its role in medical language tasks, including automated report generation and integration with healthcare systems.",
    "9 It enables the comprehensive extraction of patient data from electronic health records, laboratory results, and prior imaging studies, significantly enhancing the diagnostic process and patient care.",
    "The literature on the potential application of LLMs in VIR is, however, sparse relative to the broader discussions of opportunities and concerns provoked by AI generally but more importantly, the readily accessible LLM technologies like ChatGPT.",
    "Hence, the aim of this article is to comprehensively explore the potentials of LLMs in VIR.",
    "By reviewing the current abilities of LLMs, the aim is to highlight the potentials of this technology, outlining its current and prospective contributions to advancing clinical practices, patient outcomes, and educational activities in VIR."
